room_title: Escape room "Theft of the Texas Lone Star" by Escape Hunt in Houston
room_address: 125 West Gray Street Suite 100 Houston, TX 77019
room_description: The Sam Houston museum, dedicated to the first president of the Texas Republic, has reported a break-in. The original 1836 Texan Lone Star is missing, and what is more shocking, it looks like someone from the museum did it! Rangers, you have one hour to recover the artifact before the museum exhibit opens.
